{"arkId":"cl010112658","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010112658","modified ":"2026-02-06","title":"Astrolabe planisph\u00e9rique","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Astrolabe planisph\u00e9rique"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1821 - 1822 (1237 de l\u0027h\u00e9gire)","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1821,"endYear":1822,"imprecision":"","text":"1e quart du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"al-S\u0101hib al-Andij\u0101n\u012b","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Fabricant, facteur","authenticationType":"signature","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 11952","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"astrolabe","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Cet astrolabe est gradu\u00e9 sur son limbe d\u0027une \u00e9chelle de 360 degr\u00e9s. La m\u00e8re est inscrite d\u0027une table g\u00e9ographique circulaire. Au dos figurent une \u00e9chelle semi-circulaire de deux fois 90 degr\u00e9s ; des \u00e9chelles des ombres, un carr\u00e9 des ombres ; dans le quadrant sup\u00e9rieur gauche, un graphique des cosinus et, dans le quadrant de droite, des arcs concentriques. L\u0027araign\u00e9e formant un r\u00e9seau quasi v\u00e9g\u00e9tal porte le nom de vingt-trois \u00e9toiles. Cinq tympas pour les latitudes de 34\u00b030\u0027 \u00e0 44\u00b0 sont compl\u00e9t\u00e9s par un sixi\u00e8me, inachev\u00e9.","inscriptions":"Etiquette : \r ; \u0022557[P en exposant]\u0022 (\u00e9tiquette d\u00e9coll\u00e9e)\r ; Signature : \r ; \u0022Cet astrolabe qui ressemble au soleil a \u00e9t\u00e9 fait sous le r\u00e8gne de Sult\u0101n al-Akbar Sayyed \u0100mir Haydar Bah\u0101dur Kh\u0101n - qu\u0027All\u0101h \u00e9tende son ombre sur nos t\u00eates -, en l\u0027an 1237 de l\u0027h\u00e9gire, dans la Bonne ville de Bukh\u0101r\u0101, pr\u00e8s du tombeau empli de Lumi\u00e8re et de Gloire du tr\u00e8s grand P\u00f4le des P\u00f4les, l\u0027Incomparable Mawl\u0101n\u0101 Shar\u012bf -que sa tombe exhale les parfums -, par les efforts [\u2026] du serviteur connu sous le nom d\u0027al-S\u0101hib al-Andij\u0101n\u012b, conform\u00e9ment aux arguments de la g\u00e9om\u00e9trie et aux canons de l\u0027observation, pour fixer sur ses tympans les latitudes des diff\u00e9rentes contr\u00e9s et les positions des [\u00e9toiles] par rapport aux maisons zodiacales\u0022 (traduction de la signature, de la date et de la d\u00e9dicace, grav\u00e9e au dos, sous le carr\u00e9 des ombres)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"30","displayDimension":"30 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"1","displayDimension":"1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"20,4","displayDimension":"20,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau\/Technique : Alliage cuivreux, \u00e9tain (soudure)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : alliage cuivreux\r\nMat\u00e9riau : \u00e9tain (soudure)","placeOfCreation":"Boukhara (Asie centrale-\u003EOuzb\u00e9kistan) (Emirat de Boukhara)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Ancielle collection Nicolas Landau, Paris ; don Mme Nicolas Landau, 2002","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme Landau, Marcelle","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"M. Landau, Nicolas","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"28\/09\/2000","startYear":2000,"endYear":2000},{"type":"date du conseil artistique des mus\u00e9es nationaux","value":"04\/10\/2000","startYear":2000,"endYear":2000},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9\/d\u00e9cision","value":"02\/07\/2002","startYear":2002,"endYear":2002}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"place":[{"value":"Boukhara"}],"objectType":[{"value":"astrolabe"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Alcouffe, Daniel ; Baratte, Sophie ; Coquery, Emmanuel ; Dion, Anne ; Durand, Jannic ; Gaborit-Chopin, Danielle ; Mabille, G\u00e9rard ; Malgouyres, Philippe ; Rochebrune, Marie-Laure de ; Taburet-Delahaye, Elisabeth ; Kriser, Dani\u00e8le ; Fr\u00e9montier-Murphy, Camille ; Vittet, Jean, Nouvelles acquisitions du d\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art : 1995-2002, [Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, d\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art], Paris, R\u00e9union des mus\u00e9es nationaux, 2003","bibliographyDate":"2003","bibliographyDetail":"p. 246, cat.145","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Fr\u00e9montier-Murphy, Camille, Les Instruments de math\u00e9mathiques, XVIe-XVIIIe si\u00e8cle : cadrans solaires, astrolabes, globes, n\u00e9cessaires de math\u00e9matiques, instruments d\u0027arpentage, microscopes, Paris, R\u00e9union des mus\u00e9es nationaux (RMN), 2002","bibliographyDate":"2002","bibliographyDetail":"p. 188-189, N\u00b0 102","comparison":false}],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000112658\/0000239495_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000112658\/0000239495_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2001 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Jean-Gil